name: PDFExportPresets

properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new PDFExportPreset (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the PDFExportPreset.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the PDFExportPreset with the specified index or name.

methods.description: Returns the PDFExportPresets within the specified range.

parameters.name: from

parameters.name: to

methods.name: firstItem

methods.name: lastItem

methods.name: middleItem

methods.name: previousItem

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the PDFExportPreset that follows the desired PDFExportPreset.

methods.name: nextItem

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The PDFExportPreset whose index comes before the desired PDFExportPreset.
